{"type":"message","id":"507faf39","parentId":"b72a72de","timestamp":"2026-03-03T09:50:07.005Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"由于可用工具有限，需要先了解当前环境配置（Python、Claude Code 位置、邮件配置）才能正确实现项目。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n我明白了，我需要使用可用的工具。由于没有直接的 exec 工具，让我用 message 工具来直接创建文件。但首先，我需要了解用户的邮件配置和 Claude Code 的位置。\n\n让我先询问一些必要的信息：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_dba1627c47ff49dd901302c7","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","target":"openclaw-control-ui","message":"好的！我来帮你搭建这套 Agent 集群系统。\n\n在开始之前，我需要确认几个配置：\n\n1. **邮件通知配置**：\n   - 你的邮箱地址？\n   - SMTP 服务器（如 Gmail: smtp.gmail.com:587）？\n   - 是否需要使用应用专用密码？\n\n2. **Claude Code 位置**：\n   - 本地部署的 Claude Code 命令是什么？（例如 `claude` 还是 `npx @anthropic-ai/claude-code`？）\n   - 在哪个目录运行？\n\n3. **Git 仓库**：\n   - 目标代码库的路径？\n   - GitHub 仓库地址（用于创建 PR）？\n\n4. **会议记录**：\n   - 文件存储的位置？（例如 `~/Documents/Obsidian/`）\n\n请告诉我这些信息，我会为你创建完整的项目！"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"local-qwen2","model":"Qwen3.5-122B-A10B-FP8","usage":{"input":13571,"output":317,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":13888,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772531404610}}
