{"type":"message","id":"91f28c44","parentId":"898dffe8","timestamp":"2026-03-03T15:36:46.849Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在让我创建一些辅助脚本和配置文件，包括启动脚本、定时任务脚本、示例会议记录等。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n现在创建启动脚本和定时任务配置：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_88df4f6e91b54e1ca2bfcf0a","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"#!/bin/bash\n# start.sh - 启动整个 Agent 集群系统\n\necho \"================================\"\necho \"Agent 集群系统启动脚本\"\necho \"================================\"\n\n# 切换到项目目录\ncd /Users/lihzz/openclawCode\n\n# 检查 Python 环境\nif ! command -v python3 &> /dev/null; then\n    echo \"错误：未找到 Python3\"\n    exit 1\nfi\n\n# 创建虚拟环境（如果不存在）\nif [ ! -d \"venv\" ]; then\n    echo \"创建虚拟环境...\"\n    python3 -m venv venv\nfi\n\n# 激活虚拟环境\nsource venv/bin/activate\n\n# 安装依赖\necho \"安装依赖...\"\npip install -q python-dotenv\n\n# 检查配置文件\nif [ ! -f \"config/config.py\" ]; then\n    echo \"错误：配置文件不存在\"\n    exit 1\nfi\n\necho \"\"\necho \"可用命令:\"\necho \"  ./start.sh zoe <需求描述>  - 启动 Zoe 处理需求\"\necho \"  ./start.sh monitor        - 运行监控脚本\"\necho \"  ./start.sh daemon         - 启动守护进程（后台监控）\"\necho \"\"\n\n# 执行命令\ncase \"$1\" in\n    zoe)\n        shift\n        python agents/zoe.py \"$@\"\n        ;;\n    monitor)\n        python agents/monitor.py\n        ;;\n    daemon)\n        echo \"启动监控守护进程...\"\n        nohup python agents/monitor.py > logs/daemon.log 2>&1 &\n        echo \"守护进程已启动 (PID: $!)\"\n        ;;\n    *)\n        echo \"用法：$0 {zoe|monitor|daemon}\"\n        exit 1\n        ;;\nesac\n","path":"/Users/lihzz/openclawCode/start.sh"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"local-qwen2","model":"Qwen3.5-122B-A10B-FP8","usage":{"input":27003,"output":473,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":27476,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772552203345}}
