{"type":"message","id":"49e1bab6","parentId":"f27981e6","timestamp":"2026-03-03T15:36:50.848Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在创建示例会议记录和 README 文档。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n创建示例会议记录和 README：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6e0b494762b84b99b6ced639","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 2026-03-03 会议记录\n\n## 客户需求\n\n企业客户希望复用他们已经配置好的设置，在团队内共享。\n\n**客户原话：**\n> \"我们希望保存现有配置，而不是从头创建新的。\"\n\n## 需求拆解\n\n1. 做一个模板系统\n2. 让用户保存和编辑现有配置\n3. 支持团队内共享模板\n\n## 技术决策\n\n- 数据库：复用现有 schema，添加 `templates` 表\n- API: RESTful 设计\n- 前端：复用现有组件，添加模板管理界面\n\n## 注意事项\n\n- 客户使用的是企业版，需要支持多租户\n- 模板需要支持版本控制\n- 需要考虑权限管理（谁可以创建/使用模板）\n","path":"/Users/lihzz/openclawCode/meeting_notes/2026-03-03.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"local-qwen2","model":"Qwen3.5-122B-A10B-FP8","usage":{"input":27818,"output":241,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":28059,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772552209003}}
