{"type":"message","id":"5a779aab","parentId":"c5841a9a","timestamp":"2026-03-03T15:49:18.533Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"继续创建项目状态文件和团队配置文件，定义每个数字员工的具体职责和配置。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ca6060e5986245aab7fb119e","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 项目状态\n\n## 进行中\n\n### 每日简报系统\n- **状态**：🟡 开发中\n- **负责人**：Content\n- **进度**：30%\n- **下一步**：完成微信公众号爬取逻辑\n\n### 热点产品孵化流水线\n- **状态**：🟡 设计阶段\n- **负责人**：Zoe + Analyst\n- **进度**：20%\n- **下一步**：完成头脑风暴流程设计\n\n## 已完成\n\n- [x] 公司架构设计\n- [x] 数字员工角色定义\n- [x] 工作流设计\n\n## 待开始\n\n- [ ] 竞品分析系统（电信、移动等）\n- [ ] 自动化开发环境\n- [ ] 产品上线流程\n\n## 阻塞问题\n\n- 微信公众号爬取需要反爬策略\n- 飞书机器人需要配置 Webhook\n- 需要确定 MVP 技术栈\n","path":"/Users/lihzz/openclawCompany/PROJECT_STATUS.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"local-qwen2","model":"Qwen3.5-122B-A10B-FP8","usage":{"input":36333,"output":270,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36603,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772552956203}}
