{"type":"message","id":"538cf8b4","parentId":"08ff23b0","timestamp":"2026-03-03T16:25:55.246Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在需要配置飞书机器人，但用户还没有提供 Webhook URL，我需要询问用户并创建一个配置脚本方便他们填写。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 2️⃣ 配置飞书机器人\n\n请告诉我你的飞书机器人 Webhook URL，我会帮你配置。格式通常是：\n```\nhttps://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/bot/v2/hook/xxxxxxxxx\n```\n\n先让我创建一个配置脚本，你填入 URL 后运行：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_da7d8547938a433fbd8fd2c9","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"#!/bin/bash\n# configure_feishu.sh - 配置飞书机器人\n\necho \"🔧 配置飞书机器人\"\necho \"\"\necho \"请输入你的飞书机器人 Webhook URL:\"\necho \"(格式：https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/bot/v2/hook/xxx)\"\necho \"\"\nread -p \"Webhook URL: \" WEBHOOK_URL\n\nif [ -z \"$WEBHOOK_URL\" ]; then\n    echo \"❌ URL 不能为空\"\n    exit 1\nfi\n\n# 更新 config.py\ncd /Users/lihzz/openclawCompany\n\n# 使用 Python 更新配置\npython3 << EOF\nimport re\n\nwith open('config.py', 'r') as f:\n    content = f.read()\n\n# 更新飞书配置\nold_pattern = r'\"webhook_url\":\\s*\"\"'\nnew_pattern = f'\"webhook_url\": \"{WEBHOOK_URL}\"'\n\ncontent = re.sub(old_pattern, new_pattern, content)\n\nwith open('config.py', 'w') as f:\n    f.write(content)\n\nprint(\"✅ 飞书配置已更新\")\nEOF\n\necho \"\"\necho \"📋 配置内容:\"\ngrep -A2 \"FEISHU_CONFIG\" config.py | head -3\n\necho \"\"\necho \"🧪 测试配置...\"\n./venv/bin/python3 scripts/verify_github.py | grep -A5 \"配置总结\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"✅ 飞书机器人配置完成！\"\necho \"\"\necho \"下次运行 ./start.sh daily 时，简报会自动推送到飞书\"\n","path":"/Users/lihzz/openclawCompany/scripts/configure_feishu.sh"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"local-qwen2","model":"Qwen3.5-122B-A10B-FP8","usage":{"input":94815,"output":499,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":95314,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772555151218}}
