{"type":"message","id":"6a3c233b","parentId":"779e7e60","timestamp":"2026-03-03T17:35:07.746Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"接下来需要创建 Web 产品平台的前端模板，使用 Next.js 快速搭建情报中心、Agent 工作台等页面。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 4️⃣ 创建 Web 产品平台模板（Next.js）\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d73dc901bc7e401eb6bf6012","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 🚀 AI 产品体验平台 - Next.js 模板\n\n## 快速启动\n\n```bash\n# 创建项目\nnpx create-next-app@latest ai-lab-platform --typescript --tailwind --app\n\ncd ai-lab-platform\n\n# 添加 UI 组件\nnpx shadcn-ui@latest init\n\n# 安装依赖\nnpm install chart.js react-chartjs-2 zustand\n\n# 启动开发服务器\nnpm run dev\n```\n\n## 项目结构\n\n```\napp/\n├── page.tsx                    # 首页\n├── intelligence/               # 情报中心\n│   └── page.tsx               # 每日日报\n├── agents/                     # Agent 工作台\n│   ├── researcher/\n│   └── editor/\n├── projects/                   # 实验项目区\n│   └── [project-name]/\n└── api/                        # API 路由\n    └── v1/\n        ├── news/              # 新闻 API\n        └── report/            # 报告 API\n```\n\n## 首页组件示例\n\n```tsx\n// app/page.tsx\nexport default function Home() {\n  return (\n    <main className=\"p-8\">\n      <h1 className=\"text-4xl font-bold mb-8\">🤖 AI 产品体验平台</h1>\n      \n      <div className=\"grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3\">\n        {/* 情报中心卡片 */}\n        <a href=\"/intelligence\" className=\"p-6 border rounded-lg hover:shadow-lg\">\n          <h2 className=\"text-2xl font-bold\">📊 情报中心</h2>\n          <p className=\"text-gray-600\">每日 AI 前沿日报</p>\n        </a>\n        \n        {/* Agent 工作台卡片 */}\n        <a href=\"/agents\" className=\"p-6 border rounded-lg hover:shadow-lg\">\n          <h2 className=\"text-2xl font-bold\">🤖 Agent 工作台</h2>\n          <p className=\"text-gray-600\">查看 Agent 运行状态</p>\n        </a>\n        \n        {/* 实验项目区卡片 */}\n        <a href=\"/projects\" className=\"p-6 border rounded-lg hover:shadow-lg\">\n          <h2 className=\"text-2xl font-bold\">🧪 实验项目区</h2>\n          <p className=\"text-gray-600\">体验最新 AI 产品</p>\n        </a>\n      </div>\n    </main>\n  )\n}\n```\n\n## API 路由示例\n\n```ts\n// app/api/v1/news/route.ts\nimport { NextResponse } from 'next/server'\n\nexport async function GET() {\n  // 读取研究数据\n  const research = await import('/Users/lihzz/openclawCompany/output/research/research_20260304.json')\n  \n  return NextResponse.json({\n    success: true,\n    data: research.categorized\n  })\n}\n```\n\n## Docker 部署\n\n```dockerfile\n# Dockerfile\nFROM node:18-alpine\nWORKDIR /app\nCOPY package*.json ./\nRUN npm ci\nCOPY . .\nRUN npm run build\nEXPOSE 3000\nCMD [\"npm\", \"start\"]\n```\n\n```yaml\n# docker-compose.yml\nversion: '3.8'\nservices:\n  ai-platform:\n    build: .\n    ports:\n      - \"3000:3000\"\n    environment:\n      - TAVILY_API_KEY=${TAVILY_API_KEY}\n```\n\n## 部署到 Vercel\n\n```bash\n# 安装 Vercel CLI\nnpm i -g vercel\n\n# 部署\nvercel --prod\n```\n\n---\n\n**所有 AI 项目都必须有 Web 入口！**\n","path":"/Users/lihzz/openclawCompany/templates/nextjs-platform-template.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"local-qwen2","model":"Qwen3.5-122B-A10B-FP8","usage":{"input":162942,"output":964,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":163906,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772559299756}}
