{"type":"message","id":"4d71ce3e","parentId":"b7c539ae","timestamp":"2026-03-03T17:44:40.983Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"继续创建财务报告模板，这是 CEO 角色需要维护的核心记忆文件之一。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ceaf48fc60e544d9b5af32fa","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/lihzz/openclawCompany/memory/financial_report_template.md","content":"# 💰 财务报告 - {date}\n\n## 今日收入\n\n| 来源 | 金额 | 备注 |\n|------|------|------|\n| AI 求职信生成器 | $XXX | XX 个新订阅 |\n| AI 邮件助手 | $XXX | XX 个新订阅 |\n| 简历优化工具 | $XXX | XX 个新订阅 |\n| **总计** | **$XXX** | |\n\n## 今日支出\n\n| 项目 | 金额 | 备注 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 服务器成本 | $XX | Vercel + Railway |\n| 模型费用 | $XX | Tavily + Claude |\n| 营销费用 | $XX | 广告投放 |\n| **总计** | **$XX** | |\n\n## 净利润\n\n**今日净利润：$XXX**\n\n## 累计数据\n\n- **总用户数**: XXX\n- **月经常性收入 (MRR)**: $XXXX\n- **用户流失率**: X%\n- **获客成本 (CAC)**: $XX\n- **用户生命周期价值 (LTV)**: $XXX\n\n## 成本控制\n\n- ✅ 模型使用优化：节省$XX\n- ✅ 服务器自动伸缩：节省$XX\n- ⚠️ 待优化：[项目名]\n\n## CEO 决策\n\n- [ ] 调整 [产品] 定价\n- [ ] 增加 [渠道] 营销投入\n- [ ] 砍掉 [产品]（原因：XXX）\n\n---\n\n*由财务 Agent 生成 | CEO 审核*\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"local-qwen2","model":"Qwen3.5-122B-A10B-FP8","usage":{"input":172755,"output":408,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":173163,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772559877009}}
