{"type":"message","id":"f5a53f51","parentId":"46db408d","timestamp":"2026-03-03T17:49:48.394Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在需要创建一个监控 Dashboard 前端页面，展示每个 Agent 的工作产出。我会创建一个简洁美观的 HTML 页面，包含：\n1. 总览卡片\n2. 每个 Agent 的详细产出\n3. 三天数据对比\n4. 实时状态显示\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 2️⃣ 创建监控大盘前端页面\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4c4bbfe451f1482dafd44cb5","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/lihzz/openclawCompany/dashboard/index.html","content":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n  <title>AI 公司监控大盘 - 实时监工</title>\n  <script src=\"https://cdn.tailwindcss.com\"></script>\n  <script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js\"></script>\n  <style>\n    .agent-card { transition: all 0.3s ease; }\n    .agent-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }\n    .status-dot { animation: pulse 2s infinite; }\n    @keyframes pulse {\n      0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }\n      50% { opacity: 0.5; }\n    }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"bg-gray-50\">\n  <!-- 顶部导航 -->\n  <nav class=\"bg-white shadow-sm border-b\">\n    <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-4\">\n      <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\">\n        <div class=\"flex items-center space-x-3\">\n          <div class=\"w-10 h-10 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-purple-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center\">\n            <span class=\"text-white font-bold text-xl\">🤖</span>\n          </div>\n          <div>\n            <h1 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900\">AI 公司监控大盘</h1>\n            <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500\">实时监工 · 产出追踪 · 效率监控</p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"flex items-center space-x-4\">\n          <div class=\"text-right\">\n            <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500\">模拟周期</p>\n            <p class=\"font-semibold text-gray-900\">2026-03-01 ~ 2026-03-03</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"w-3 h-3 bg-green-500 rounded-full status-dot\"></div>\n          <span class=\"text-sm text-green-600 font-medium\">系统运行中</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </nav>\n\n  <!-- 总览统计 -->\n  <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-6\">\n    <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 mb-8\">\n      <div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm p-6 border-l-4 border-blue-500\">\n        <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\">\n          <div>\n            <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 mb-1\">总任务完成</p>\n            <p class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900\">18</p>\n            <p class=\"text-xs text-green-600 mt-1\">↑ 100% 完成率</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center\">\n            <span class=\"text-2xl\">✅</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm p-6 border-l-4 border-purple-500\">\n        <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\">\n          <div>\n            <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 mb-1\">项目上线</p>\n            <p class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900\">1</p>\n            <p class=\"text-xs text-green-600 mt-1\">AI 情报中心</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-purple-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center\">\n            <span class=\"text-2xl\">🚀</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm p-6 border-l-4 border-green-500\">\n        <div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\">\n          <div>\n            <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 mb-1\">代码提交</p>\n            <p class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900\">55</p>\n            <p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1\">3 天总计</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-cent