{"type":"message","id":"637b822f","parentId":"a8fe92b2","timestamp":"2026-03-03T17:50:01.820Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在需要创建一个启动脚本来运行本地服务器，让用户可以访问监控大盘页面。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 4️⃣ 创建启动脚本\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ee6b95f6627e40bba3080e3b","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/lihzz/openclawCompany/start_dashboard.sh","content":"#!/bin/bash\n# 启动监控大盘\n\necho \"🚀 启动 AI 公司监控大盘...\"\n\n# 检查 Python\nif ! command -v python3 &> /dev/null; then\n    echo \"❌ 未找到 Python3\"\n    exit 1\nfi\n\n# 启动简单的 HTTP 服务器\ncd /Users/lihzz/openclawCompany/dashboard\n\necho \"\"\necho \"📊 监控大盘已启动！\"\necho \"======================\"\necho \"\"\necho \"访问地址：\"\necho \"  http://localhost:8080\"\necho \"\"\necho \"功能：\"\necho \"  ✅ 实时查看所有 Agent 工作产出\"\necho \"  ✅ 三天数据对比\"\necho \"  ✅ 项目进度追踪\"\necho \"  ✅ 效率趋势图表\"\necho \"\"\necho \"按 Ctrl+C 停止服务\"\necho \"======================\"\necho \"\"\n\n# 使用 Python 启动服务器\npython3 -m http.server 8080\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"local-qwen2","model":"Qwen3.5-122B-A10B-FP8","usage":{"input":186131,"output":297,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":186428,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772560196815}}
